Introduction

S2 (에스투) was a six-member girl group under CLIMIX Entertainment. They debuted on August 24, 2017 with their first single "Honeya". Their name is a combination of "S" (for Serendipity) and "2" for the members and fans to meet together and bring 'unexpected luck and love'. They are presumably disbanded due to inactivity on their SNS accounts since February 2018.
